---
import PhoneMockup from './PhoneMockup.astro';
---

<section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-nexus-respect/5 via-white to-nexus-creative/5 relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Decorative Background -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-5">
    <div class="absolute top-20 right-20 w-72 h-72 bg-nexus-creative rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-20 left-20 w-96 h-96 bg-nexus-respect rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-bf-black mb-6"> O <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-nexus-respect via-bf-purple to-nexus-creative">Trio Imbatível</span> para Suas Vendas de Black Friday!
      </h2>
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Na NEXUS, sabemos que cada canal tem seu poder único para engajar. <strong>Juntos</strong>, eles formam a estratégia perfeita para você dominar a Black Friday com altíssima taxa de conversão.
      </p>
      <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-nexus-respect via-bf-purple to-nexus-creative mx-auto mt-6"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Trio Grid -->
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
      <!-- Bloco 3.1: SMS -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 border-t-4 border-nexus-respect group hover:scale-105">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-nexus-respect to-blue-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 10h.01M12 10h.01M16 10h.01M9 16H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v8a2 2 0 01-2 2h-5l-5 5v-5z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-nexus-tech">SMS</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-nexus-respect font-semibold">Alcance e Velocidade Incomparáveis</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Com <strong class="text-nexus-respect">98% de taxa de abertura</strong>, o SMS é a garantia de que sua mensagem é vista. Perfeito para lembretes de última hora, códigos de cupom exclusivos e comunicados urgentes que exigem ação imediata do cliente.
        </p>

        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-nexus-respect flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-gray-700">Entrega instantânea</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-nexus-respect flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-gray-700">Alcance universal</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-nexus-respect flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-gray-700">Ideal para urgência</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Bloco 3.3: RCS (Carro-Chefe) NO MEIO -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-nexus-creative/10 to-nexus-respect/10 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 border-t-4 border-nexus-creative group hover:scale-105 relative overflow-hidden">
        <!-- Badge Destaque -->
        <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 bg-bf-gold text-bf-black text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full animate-pulse-slow">
          CARRO-CHEFE
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-nexus-creative to-nexus-respect rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 18h.01M8 21h8a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H8a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-nexus-tech">RCS</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-nexus-creative-dark font-semibold">A Revolução Visual que Converte!</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Diga adeus às mensagens comuns! Com o RCS, suas ofertas <strong class="text-nexus-creative-dark">ganham vida</strong> e suas mensagens se tornam mini-sites interativos. Imagine: carrosséis de produtos, vídeos de ofertas, botões de 'Comprar Agora', mapas – tudo direto no celular do cliente!
        </p>

        <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-nexus-creative-dark flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-gray-700">Carrosséis de produtos interativos</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-nexus-creative-dark flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-gray-700">Botões de ação instantânea</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-nexus-creative-dark flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-gray-700">Vídeos e mídia ultra rica</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-nexus-creative-dark flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-gray-700">Localização e mapas integrados</span>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <!-- Badge Agentes Compartilhados -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-bf-black to-nexus-tech text-white rounded-lg p-4 mt-4">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-bf-gold" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-sm font-bold text-bf-gold">EXCLUSIVO BLACK FRIDAY</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm">
            <strong>Agentes Compartilhados</strong> com tema de BF PRONTOS para sua empresa usar, mesmo sem ter um agente próprio!
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Bloco 3.2: WhatsApp -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 border-t-4 border-green-500 group hover:scale-105">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500 to-green-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.890-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-nexus-tech">WhatsApp</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-green-600 font-semibold">O Poder do Relacionamento e Engajamento</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Conecte-se com seus clientes onde eles já estão! Envie <strong class="text-green-600">catálogos visuais</strong>, vídeos de produtos, áudios e construa um relacionamento que gera vendas. Ideal para atendimento rápido, triagem de vendas e campanhas segmentadas.
        </p>

        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-gray-700">Mídia rica (fotos, vídeos, áudios)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-gray-700">Atendimento conversacional</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-gray-700">Alto engajamento e confiança</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Phone Mockup + Summary -->
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mt-16">
      <!-- Phone Mockup -->
      <div class="flex justify-center lg:order-1">
        <PhoneMockup variant="rcs" />
      </div>

      <!-- Summary/Strategy -->
      <div class="lg:order-2">
        <h3 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-nexus-tech mb-6">
          A Estratégia Perfeita: <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-nexus-respect via-green-500 to-nexus-creative">Juntos</span> São Imbatíveis!
        </h3>

        <div class="space-y-4 mb-8">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 bg-white/50 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-nexus-respect rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 text-white font-bold">
              1
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-nexus-tech mb-1">SMS para Urgência</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Dispare ofertas relâmpago, cupons exclusivos e lembretes de última hora.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 bg-white/50 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-green-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 text-white font-bold">
              2
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-nexus-tech mb-1">WhatsApp para Relacionamento</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Tire dúvidas, envie catálogos personalizados e construa confiança.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 bg-white/50 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-nexus-creative rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 text-white font-bold">
              3
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-nexus-tech mb-1">RCS para Conversão</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Apresente produtos de forma visual, interativa e irresistível - direto para a compra!</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-nexus-respect/10 to-nexus-creative/10 border-l-4 border-nexus-creative p-6 rounded-r-xl">
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            <strong class="text-nexus-tech">O resultado?</strong> Uma experiência completa que atinge seus clientes em todos os momentos da jornada de compra, maximizando suas vendas na Black Friday como nunca!
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
